from scapy.all import *
packets = rdpcap("capture.pcap") for pkt in packets:
if IP in pkt:
ip = pkt[IP] original = ip.chksum del ip.chksum
new = IP(bytes(ip)).chksum

print("Packet:", pkt.summary()) print("Original IP checksum:",
hex(original))
print("Calculated IP checksum:", hex(new)) print("Valid:", original == new)
print("-" * 40)
